{"id": "1412622882378485791", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "content": "and while I'm at it, I'm mostly here for gameplay stuff, so usually I don't touch the dialogue but here it's pretty goofy... How do these sound?\n\noriginal: [Attack the black cat]\n> \"Heh, insignificant human, you made the wrong choice.\"\n> The black cats coldly stared at you, suddenly attacking.\n> \"You must pay the price—of course, we also respect the strong.\"\n\nmy fix: [Attack the Cat]\n> \"Heh, petty human, you made the wrong choice.\"\n> The black cats stared coldly at you, and suddenly retaliate.\n> \"Though we have respect for the brave, you must pay the price.\"\n\noriginal: [Meow like a cat]\n> \"Shut up, shut up, you sound terrible.\"\n> The black cat humanoid covers its ears humanizingly.\n> \"Human, your cat language is really poor, what a chaotic mess you're saying!\"\n> Though it says this, the expression of the black cat softens.\n> \"Given that you meowed to please me, here's a gift for you.\"\n> \"As for the content of the gift, it depends on your luck.\"\n\nmy fix: [Meow Like a Cat]\n> \"Shut up, shut up, you sound terrible.\"\n> The black cat covers its ears with its paws in a uniquely human manner.\n> \"Human, your cat-speak is very poor, what you're saying is a chaotic mess!\"\n> Though it says this, the expression of the black cat softens.\n> \"Given that you meowed to please me, here's a gift for you.\"\n> \"As for the content of the gift, it depends on your luck.\"", "timestamp": "2025-09-03T02:19:00.423000+00:00"}
